casebody.data:
George E. Tibball v. Carol Jean Tibball (13486)

O’Connell, Heiman and Spear, Js.

Submitted on briefs January 6 decision released January 24, 1995 Wesley W. Horton, Karen L. Murdock arid John Reed, legal intern, filed a brief for the appellant (plaintiff). Joy Kony Peshkin and Bruce A. Foodman filed a brief for the appellee (defendant). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
